OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand strong winds spreading north on
OL,7,FSaturday with a risk of gales.
OL,8,FBlustery showers with gale risk easing
OL,9,Fon Sunday. Mostly dry with sunny
OL,10,Fspells Monday, windy near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
